# M6 P01 audit — jetpack thrust test.
#
# Pre-fix (Phase 5 bug): pose_write_to_particles zeroed velocity every
# tick, so jet impulse couldn't accumulate. Mech only got 1 tick of
# upward thrust per gravity tick → ~36 px/sec instead of the design
# thrust of -16 m/s² ≈ -480 px/s² acceleration.
#
# Post-fix: mech climbs rapidly while jet held, then falls under
# gravity when released.

window 1280 720
seed   77 34
out    build/shots/m6_jet_test

loadout Trooper "Pulse Rifle" Sidearm Light Standard
spawn_at 640 920
mouse    1000 360

# Hold jet for ~1.5 seconds (90 ticks) then release.
at  10 press jet
at  10 shot t010_jet_start
at  30 shot t030_climbing
at  60 shot t060_higher
at  90 shot t090_one_and_a_half_sec
at  90 release jet
at 110 shot t110_release_then_fall
at 150 shot t150_falling_back
at 200 shot t200_landed
contact_sheet jet_sheet cols 4
at 220 end
